game.CardCollection
Class AbstractPile

java.lang.Object
  game.CardCollection.AbstractPile
Direct Known Subclasses:
BattlePile, DiscardPile, DistancePile, DrawPile, SafetyPile, SpeedPile
public abstract class AbstractPile
extends java.lang.Object

This card represent a collection of cards. Extensions of this class could be card collection with special characteristics. To this end, this class contain a method named getType which describe the compatible type. Plz note that there is no transformer to the "type" attribute. (Children override the accessor by returning type appropriately)
